The magazine presents a range of creative productions, including the creation of characters who tell local stories with societal values ​​emanating from the Arab reality, and some of the characters produced in Japan, which we will present with an innovative local template that fits our culture and thought. It provides an enjoyable and safe experience, with high-end content and a simple Arabic language.

Support, communication between authors and developers with players in the Telegram channel: @sloword_app

What we will work on in the coming years. Expanding the list of questions in the current 25 languages. Both within one language and between language pairs. Improving segregation of words by difficulty level. Elements of training for beginners. Design of the application in a magazine format, where you choose the pages. The application already works as a monthly magazine, but this is not easy to guess. We would appreciate your feedback with ideas and suggestions!

Any of the puzzles in the app can be solved in one or two languages. The language is selected separately for questions and answers, as in Millionaire or Find words in a circle. Separately for answers and hints, as in Find words in a grid. Or for words on the left and right, as in Find pairs. It is easier to play in one native language than in two. The two-language mode is suitable for those who know a foreign language at a decent level. Learning a language “from scratch” in Sloword is not an easy task.

Difficulty levels for all puzzles are set to "Mix" by default. The mix is a gradual alternation of easy, medium and hard levels every 10 puzzles. If desired, you can set a fixed difficulty for the puzzles.

25 languages are active in the game: English, Russian, French, Spanish, Portuguese/Brazilian, German, Italian, Japanese, Chinese, Arabic, Turkish, Swedish, Ukrainian, Georgian, Tatar, Chechen, Bashkir, Chuvash, Avar, Lezgin, Kumyk, Lak, Tabasaran, Dargin, Ingush.
The list of languages in development can be seen by scrolling through the feed in the “My languages” section.

Every month, 100 new puzzles in three difficulty levels in each of the 4 games are automatically downloaded (Settings - Other settings - New puzzles slider must be opened). Puzzles older than 1 year are deleted. Update is only for the selected languages. You can download the puzzles and solve them without the Internet.

Friends of the Sloword Club solve puzzles without advertising and with free use of hints.

Introducing the Raseef22 App: Empowering Arab Voices through Independent Journalism
In an age where information is power, the Raseef22 App delivers independent journalism at your fingertips. We are dedicated to providing you with an unfiltered, firsthand view of the Arabic-speaking world's socio-political landscape. Raseef22 is committed to fostering a well-informed and engaged citizenry. Our app makes this easy, delivering a seamless user experience, personalized content, and the ability to follow topics, journalists and countries of your interest.

Your Gateway to Insightful Journalism
At Raseef22, we understand the importance of quality journalism, especially when the truth is often obscured by a flood of other information. Our app serves as your gateway to insightful, fact-based reporting on the issues that matter most to you. From politics to culture, economics to human rights, we provide in-depth analyses, opinion pieces, and on-the-ground reporting that bring you closer to the heart of the Arabic-speaking world.

The Power of Personalization
We understand that no two readers are alike, and your content should reflect your unique interests. That's why our app offers personalized content recommendations tailored to your preferences. Whether you're passionate about regional politics, arts and culture, or lifestyle, our app ensures you stay connected to the untold stories that resonate most with you. Your personalized feed evolves as your interests do, delivering a curated experience with each use. 

Seamless User Experience
We believe that accessing information should be effortless, and that's why the Raseef22 App has a user-friendly, intuitive and smooth interface. Navigating articles, exploring different sections, and customizing your reading experience has never been easier. Our app guarantees that you spend less time searching for content, and more time engaging with the stories that matter to you.

Your Personal Space
With our Personal Space feature, you have the power to save articles, revisit comments and follow your choice of countries and journalists. Whether it's a thought-provoking op-ed, a captivating feature, or an in-depth investigative report, you can access your saved articles and comments at any time. This feature makes it convenient to revisit articles, share them with friends, or simply enjoy them at your leisure, allowing you to build your own library of knowledge.

Breaking Down Barriers
Raseef22 is committed to breaking down the barriers that often limit access to information. We provide our readers with a platform to explore a diverse range of voices and perspectives, ensuring that every story is told. From marginalized to unheard voices, we strive to amplify stories that often go unnoticed, creating a more inclusive media landscape for all.

Stay Connected, Stay Informed
The Raseef22 App is not just a source of news; it's your tool for staying connected in an ever-changing world. We keep you informed with real-time alerts and push notifications, ensuring that you are up-to-date with the happenings of the Arab-speaking world. 

Join the NasRaseef Community
As a member of NasRaseef, you are not just a passive reader; you're part of a vibrant and engaged community that shares in your commitment to quality journalism and informed dialogue. Connect with fellow readers, engage in thoughtful discussions, and share your own insights through our interactive platform. Your support empowers us to continue delivering independent journalism that matters.

Privacy and Security
Your privacy is our utmost concern. The Raseef22 App is designed with strict data security measures to protect your personal information. 

Together, we can make a difference, one story at a time.
